Package: ai-cli
Version: 3.1.7.3
Architecture: all
Maintainer: minerofthesoal <https://github.com/minerofthesoal/ai-cli>
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Depends: bash (>= 5.0), python3 (>= 3.10), curl, git
Recommends: python3-pip, ffmpeg, jq
Suggests: gh, nodejs, npm
Homepage: https://github.com/minerofthesoal/ai-cli
Description: AI CLI — local + cloud LLM terminal toolkit
 Unified terminal interface for local and cloud AI models.
 Supports GGUF (llama.cpp), OpenAI, Claude, Gemini, Groq,
 Together, and Mistral APIs. Includes TTM/MTM model training,
 RLHF with DPO/PPO/GRPO, Canvas v3 TUI workspace, and 195
 curated model recommendations.
